---
title: Hawaiian-Style Pineapple Chicken with Sweet Peppers and Jasmine Rice
description: This dish is inspired by the East-meets-West cuisine of Hawaii! Tender chicken is stir-fried with peppers and pineapple then tossed with teriyaki sauce. It's oh-so-sticky and sure to be a new fave.
